@AdamWr 
Do you have an iOS device to check the page? With the AdGuard Extension, it was always hided fine. But for about a week, it stopped working.
I have tested 2 iPhones and an iPad and it doesn't work anymore. Any other page is filtered fine. And the filters still works fine on Windows desktop. What can be the reason?

